<div class="entry-content"><p>The Spring 2018 issue of <em>Buddhadharma:
The Practitioner's Quarterly </em> is available now. Inside, you’ll find the Madhyamaka view of the two truths, unpacked by Dzogchen Ponlop Rinpoche, a guided tour by Josh Bartok of the subtle practice of <em>shikantaza,</em> an in-depth look at Dogen and his understanding of “being–time,” and more.
